My Chelsea In Bloom Flower Workshop is now LIVE! 🍄🌺🌷

My next flower workshop will be a really special one, hosted in Partnership and with Gaucho on Sloane Avenue, Chelsea, on Tuesday 23rd May, 11:00am - 1:00pm to celebrate Chelsea in Bloom week. Tickets will be £95 per person.

This seasonal workshop is designed to celebrate the very best of May flowers 🌺 Everyone attending will learn how to create their own luscious statement summer bell vase bursting with scent and colour, using tall delphiniums and blush garden peonies, ready to take home with you… These flower arrangements are designed perfectly for any entrance hallway, a kitchen Worktop or to enjoy ready for entertaining at home! The perfect way to bring Chelsea in Bloom into the home. 

Tickets are £95pp, which includes all fresh flowers and foliage, a vase, and complimentary champagne to enjoy throughout.

This workshop is now live and available to book on the Gaucho website (the booking link is in my bio) 🌺

https://gauchorestaurants.com/gaucho-in-bloom/ 

Xxxx ❤️
